PGXN,is,a,central,distribution,system,for,open,source,PostgreSQL,extension,libraries,The,PGXN,API,is,an,index,API,that,distributes,metadata,about,PostgreSQL,extensions,to,distribution,mirror,sites,using,JSON,All,mirror,sites,provide,a,set,of,API,functions,including,browsing,distributions,by,tag,and,user,as,well,as,retrieving,a,list,of,mirror,sites,among,other,information,related,to,distributions,The,central,API,servers,are,the,only,ones,with,specific,functionality,that,includes,full,text,search,source,viewing,and,accessing,a,list,of,all,PGXN,users